{"tid":498202,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7年喇 點樣先可以放得低？","createTime":"2017-12-13T14:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T15:30:49.000Z","uid":111815,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af432ccf569c5f698979d0ab8a0f9b4bbb30ad48","tid":498202,"uid":111815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"我鍾意咗佢7年喇，係得佢我先知道咩係愛一個人<br />\n我咁大個人，鍾意過好多人，但愛真係得佢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放低又拎起，拎起又放低<br />\n我已經單身咗好多年，我覺得自己好難再搵到個我可以再咁愛佢嘅人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同佢係一個好好好好既朋友<br />\n我鍾意佢咁耐，佢身邊都好多異性<br />\n呢幾年佢都拍過幾次拖<br />\n最辛苦係我一直喺佢身邊，我要同佢分享感情生活<br />\n而我既身份，係好難去表達我既感受<br />\n我更加知道我同佢呢一世都唔會有可能<br />\n好想各位連登仔可以屌醒我<br />\n我要點樣先可以澈澈底底咁放低呢個人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4e6d869e467d713138f3193e4ea4133633eb87","tid":498202,"uid":111815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"我又post錯台，應該放感情台先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa388e1d3b584697422f39d3196dcc9a559f069","tid":498202,"uid":131553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"去叫雞，就會醒㗎啦你。"},{"pid":"ccae8dad88798c760fdef17f46aadca774b1bd14","tid":498202,"uid":141767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"樓主巴定絲"},{"pid":"140ab6b9d7810d68e4ec310d02942ee28cb3df36","tid":498202,"uid":111815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主巴定絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係一個好傻好蠢嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e05e3cf098560f8a1271f9ef31a9de3741305de","tid":498202,"uid":111815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去叫雞，就會醒㗎啦你。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對住啲雞都冇欲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}